woman, making sure that there's a safety net

00:51:18.840 --> 00:51:26.120
for making mistakes and that you as a leader
can reveal that you make mistakes, that you

00:51:26.120 --> 00:51:28.690
do things and it's ok.

00:51:28.690 --> 00:51:32.350
Creating that safety net.

